# /etc/gitpkg/pkglist — known packages
# Format: name|description
# Used by 'gitpkg search' and tab-completion
# Package names must match repository names under configured mirrors
gitpkg|Git-based package manager
atomic-upgrade|Atomic upgrade system for archlinux
subs2srs|A tool for flashcards creation (Mono version)
subs2srs-gtk3|A tool for flashcards creation (Gtk3 version)
hardened_malloc|GrapheneOS hardened_malloc — packaged for system-wide preloading
fetch|minimal system information tool with gitpkg integration
transformers_ocr|An OCR tool that uses Transformers
btrfs-file-history|Track file and directory lifecycle across btrfs snapshots
verify-lib|Validates shell library files before sourcing — compiled binary to break the bootstrap problem
bwrap-common|Reusable bubblewrap sandbox helpers for shell wrappers
